    <h3 class="title"><a href="/towards-frameless-clockless-video#comment-10877" class="active">Your proposed protocol is</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by corysama (not verified) on Tue, 2009-11-10 21:57.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>Your proposed protocol is pretty similar to a simple GPU command buffer protocol.  Reading it gives me the feeling that what you are going to end up with is duplicating or moving the GPU into the display device --effectively stretching the PCI-Express bus over a DVI cable.</p>
<p>Whether or not that's a good idea.. I have no comment.  I just wanted to mention which wheel your invention looks like from a distance.</p>
